{"id": "1420078282228895835", "channel_id": "1326453763355185215", "author_id": "446266944723746818", "author_name": "mami7284", "content": "It and Arknights have different priorities since it's more focused on eldritch horrors while Arknights is more focused on comparitively mundane societal horrors (even if it does get crazy sometimes).", "timestamp": "2025-09-23T16:04:06.262000+00:00", "type": 19, "mentions": ["620741171358072866"], "reply_to": "1420045531362889809"}
